As shown in Figs. 2g and S20b, the b values reveal that the electrochemical reaction kinetics of both MoS2 and MoS2/PANI cathodes are composed of capacitive and diffusion controlled. At a specified scan rate, the capacitive contribution and the diffusion-controlled contribution can be further evaluated according to Eq. 2 [48, 49]:2iv=k1v+k2v1/2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
